name: Rats!
description:
For my friends! 

A self portrait from 2019, one of the first images I created digitally and used as a business card in my tattooing life. Now edited and animated as a video to enjoy. 

 Rats are intelligent, loving beings. One could be so lucky to be involved in a rats life. 

For love. For Light and for dark. For without dark, there could be no light.
Keep Creating. Live with intention.

2,256 x 2,160
30 sec
